In competitive public speaking (Forensics), students must give Impromptu speeches. Students are given a random quotation and a total of seven minutes to prepare and deliver a speech. "Prep Time" is limited to a maximum of three minutes; "Speaking Time" is a minimum of four minutes.

This iOS app allows students to practice Impromptu Speeches by giving random quotations and timing the speech. Per convention, the app counts up during prep time and down during speaking time.The app includes several helpful features, like indicating a speech going overtime. 